data.description: You are not going to want to miss this opportunity to live on Lake Dow! Enjoy the beauty of this all brick home situated cove side with docking rights. As you step inside you'll notice the freshly refinished hardwood floors in the foyer and throughout the main floor. A sophisticated dining room with classic chair rail molding is perfect for hosting gatherings. The main level features a spacious primary bedroom retreat featuring a charming tray ceiling and an en suite bathroom designed for relaxation, complete a jetted tub, separate shower, double vanity and a generous sized walk-in closet.  Gather in the family room where vaulted ceilings accentuate the space and striking stone fireplace. The heart of the home lies in the kitchen, featuring a granite countertops, center v shaped island, ample cabinetry, a convenient pantry, and a sunny breakfast area. Adjacent is a charming keeping room complete with its own fireplace.  Venture upstairs to discover three additional bedrooms, and a Jack n Jill bathroom accessible to all three bedrooms. The full finished basement provides endless possibilities for entertainment or can be used as an in-law suite. There is one bedroom with a nice size walk in closet, one full bathroom, two additional rooms can be used as an office and a sprawling room equipped with a pool table and a convenient small size kitchen/bar area.  Outside enjoy the serenity of lakeside living, private backyard leading to the lake. Don't miss your chance to experience lakeside living at its finest. Schedule your tour today and make this home your reality!
